summary: A beautiful nord female preset to use with RaceMenu.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=4]Hello. This is my first mod. Hopefully it works, and you enjoy it :)[/size]


[size=3]Vixen is a seductive, red-headed, assassin-type dragonborn. At least, she is in my game. You can play her any way you want, for it is just a preset. Who knows, maybe in the future I will upload an actual savegame file? Only time will tell.[/size]

[size=3]This preset is made to work on a nord female, and you can try it on other races if you wish but I have no guarantees for how it will turn out. I can confirm, [/size][i]it does work on wood elves[/i][size=3], [/size][u]but[/u][size=3] the result is [/size][b]not pretty.[/b][/center]

[b][size=5]REQUIRED MODS:[/size][/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url][size=3], [/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056/?]Mikan Eyes[/url][size=3], [/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url]

[b][size=5]RECOMMENDED MODS[/size][/b][size=3] [to make character exactly like in the screenshots]:[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30936/?]Realvision ENB[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70834/?]Demoniac Texture[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/?]UNP BLESSED BODY- UNPB REDUX PROJECT[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72825/?]Maevan2's eye brows[/url]
[font=Times New Roman][size=5] [/size]
[b][size=3]
[/size][/b][/font][b][size=3]CREDITS:[/size][/b]
